      <title>特斯拉交付量超出预期，但仍低于去年同期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-02/tesla-deliveries-top-estimates-still-down-from-year-ago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉第二季度交付量超出预期。埃隆·马斯克的公司交付了近 44.4 万辆汽车，但销量较去年同期下降了 4.8%。艾德·拉德洛报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-02/tesla-deliveries-top-estimates-still-down-from-year-ago</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:09:22 GMT</pubDate>
