    <item>
      <title>飓风贝丽尔在加勒比地区留下毁灭性的痕迹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-02/hurricane-beryl-leaves-trail-of-destruction-in-caribbean</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，飓风贝丽尔横扫加勒比海东南部，造成严重破坏。随着巴巴多斯的风力减弱，居民们开始查看损失情况。街道上布满了被风和汹涌的海浪吹散的碎石。在圣文森特，强风掀翻了屋顶。贝丽尔首先在格林纳达登陆，可能会袭击牙买加，然后进入墨西哥湾。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-02/hurricane-beryl-leaves-trail-of-destruction-in-caribbean</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:01:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行不需要服务业通胀率达到 2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/lagarde-says-ecb-doesn-t-need-services-inflation-at-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行不需要服务业通胀——这是政策制定者在决定将利率降低多少以放缓至 2% 的目标时关注的重点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/lagarde-says-ecb-doesn-t-need-services-inflation-at-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:57:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
